<br>
Bringing me back to my original question.  What is it exactly that you're delivering at a lower frequency to a higher frequency system?  Maybe your choice of terms was simply misleading and you meant to say something like &quot;Delivering precise, low-voltage power to GHz systems&quot;?  Using Hertz as a measure of power just makes no sense.<br>
